    <h1 class="text-title">Team MapleByte for G20 Disaster Risk Reduction (DRR) Hackathon 2025</h1>
    <img style="margin-left: -150px;margin-top: -145px;" width="120" height="120" src="/G20_DRR_logo_compressed.webp" alt="G20 DRR Logo (unofficial)" />
    <p>
